FBIS3-35280 "drnes036_j_94007" FBIS-NES-94-036 Document Type:Daily Report 23 Feb 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Clashes Reported Between North, South; Reaction Noted Ambush Reported 22 Feb NC2202180394 Paris AFP in English 1754 GMT 22 Feb 94 NC2202180394 Paris AFP Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Amman, Feb 22 (AFP)--Northern Yemeni troops on Tuesday ambushed and killed 15 soldiers from the rival south, a Yemeni official said here. The ambush was sprung by a northern brigade at al-'Amaliqah, based in the Abyan region of southern Yemen, the south Yemeni official said in Jordan where the rival leaders signed a reconciliation accord on Sunday. There was no confirmation from the north.
